{"tid":1914472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[入境處訓醒未?]クルーズ船の香港の男性が死亡　乗船者で7人目","createTime":"2020-03-07T14:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T14:21:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24ac57b8905178f57e59dd5a85710f427d10e2f0","tid":1914472,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN3774W0N37ULBJ005.html?iref=comtop_8_03\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Farticles%2FASN3774W0N37ULBJ005.html%3Firef%3Dcomtop_8_03&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=28cc67f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN3774W0N37ULBJ005.html?iref=comtop_8_03</a><br />\n<br />\n大型クルーズ船ダイヤモンド・プリンセス号に乗っていた香港の男性が6日死亡したと、厚生労働省が7日発表した。クルーズ船の乗船者で国内で死亡したのは7人目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名鑽石公主號香港乘客於日本留醫期間死亡，是船上感染中第七名死亡乘客"},{"pid":"543295745f5362d80e60cc19b971871a750bd369","tid":1914472,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c65938f42f8a3086700add5b7ce638833199a8a","tid":1914472,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebf5a77d1095a5d3224a3c46294820f070744aa","tid":1914472,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"幾多歲..."}]}